text: New England or New England North West is the name given to a generally undefined region in the north of the state of New South Wales, Australia. It is about inland, that includes the Northern Tablelands (or New England Tablelands) and the North West Slopes regions.Shaw, John H., "Collins Australian Encyclopedia", William Collins Pty Ltd., Sydney, 1984, == References == == Other websites == *New South Wales Forecast Areas Map Category:Regions of New South Wales
title: New England (New South Wales)
